+ * Coverage matrix (verified on Node 25.9.0):
+ *
+ *   PoC #1 (Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptor → .value)            blocked
+ *   PoC #2 (ho.getOwnPropertyDescriptor → .value)                blocked
