+ *    subclasses) so the `new pp.constructor(s)` chain cannot even reach the
+ *    real constructor.
+ * 3. Every handler trap method (`get`, `set`, `apply`, `construct`, ...)
+ *    short-circuits when called on a `this` that is not a registered handler
